  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 11, 2025</p>

  <p>At SmartCalcHub, we value your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We do not collect any personal information directly. Our calculators run entirely in your browser.</p>

  <h2>2. Cookies</h2>
  <p>We may use third-party tools like Google AdSense that use cookies to show relevant ads. These cookies do not personally identify you.</p>

  <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We may use Google AdSense or analytics tools in the future. These services may collect anonymized data. You can review <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank">Google’s Privacy Policy here</a>.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Protection</h2>
  <p>Since we don’t store user data, there is no risk of your data being shared or exposed.</p>

  <h2>5. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions, contact us at: <a href="mailto:your@email.com">your@email.com</a></p>

  <p>By using SmartCalcHub, you agree to this privacy policy.</p>
